values: Well, I went to ozzfest on wednesday and that fuckin rocked. Disturbed put on the best show, I also got to meet them and got my ticket and my cd signed by them, it was pretty fuckin sweet. Also saw atreyu, black label society, dragon force (they sucked), norma jean, and system of adown. I would have just gone for disturbed and left though, but the other bands were decent. Oh yeah, and for all you inde/punk rock fans out there I have one thing to say to you FUCK THAT SHIT FUCK THAT SHIT FUCK THAT SHIT

Am I alive or dead, asleep or awake, i just don't know what is going on right now, i feel really depressed most of the time, I am starting to hit the bottle again, and I need to stop b4 i get addicted, someone please help me, this is the third night in a row, oh well, i am really tired, I am sorry if this didnt make sense.

I don't know why i have these feelings toward someone else, i just do, something I just couldnt let go. I really feel bad, i already have someone to love, why should I feel love toward someone else, I just don't think i have gotten over this person, whenever i hang around them, I feel like everything is allright why couldnt i have them all for myself, damnit they mean so much to me, it's not fair, there is someone else i love and not the person that i am with right now.

Well, i finally have some plans for my future. I am going to try and be out of lcc by the end of 2007 and then be on to grand valley state university, hopefully there, i will be able to continue my schooling and end up majoring in computer sciences. I really feel good about this, and I know if I work hard enough, I can achieve this goal. I really really hope that I can go to that college, there is just something about it, I don't really know, the campus is really nice, and it just seems like there is a good vibe coming from that place. Well, I am going to achieve this goal, and I am not going to let anyone or anything stop me. Well, I guess thats all for now.
Somethings wrong, i already have someone, i shouldnt feel this way again, i have someone to love, why do i get these feelings towards someone.

I can't sleep, too much hatred, towards everyone and everything, and just annoyed, slipped last night talking about jafax in front of kevin, so now he wants to go, i really don't want him to go because he is cool around me and david, but when he gets around other people, he acts like a fucking idiot, so if he goes, i won't and thats how it is i guess. Well i will still go, i will just go with liz, and i don't even know if i am going to go as sephiroth or not. Oh well, i guess thats all for now.

Well, i started classes yesterday, i had a math class that goes from 12:10 to 2:00 so it is kind of nice to get out of work early. I also had a class tonight that runs from 6:10 to 10:00, but tonight we only had an hour of class because we were just doing the introduction part, it is going to be really boring, but i guess i will have to deal with it. I might be going to see the new underworld movie on friday so if ne one wants to go just let me know and maybe we can go. Thats all for now, I think i am going to go get drunk now so bye byes.

Well, my new years eve was really good, i got to hang out with david and mike and dani. It was nice to see dani again, i havent seen her in a long time, and she got me the coolest christmas gift ever, a mario video game for my key chain, it is SWEET. I have to get her something now because i feel bad that i didnt get her anything for christmas, same with david. I did however get my xbox 360 which is awesome, well thats all for now i guess bye byes.

Well, i had to go to work today, wich really sucked, because it's the day after christmas and i am suppose to be able to play with all the cool stuff i got yesterday, oh well, i love money too much to quit, i also have to check on my classes so i can see why i am not getting my bill, i hate dealing with the morons there, it's like they don't even want to do anything except sit there all day and talk to people online, wich i have seen more than once. Oh well, theres nothing i can do about it, i had a good christmas though, it was alot of fun, and my cousins weren't that bad ^_^ so thats all good. Well just let me know how everyones christmas was.

But i have too, it really sux, that is the one thing that i hate the most, if i have to go in for surgery, fine. Just don't fuck with my teeth, i hate it hate it hate it :P Oh well, at least i should get out of unloading the truck tommorow, so that should be nice, but i will be hurting the entire next day, oh well, i will live. I went and saw chronicles of narnia with my friend danielle giermann on friday, it was a very good movie, and i will probably end up buying it when it comes out, oh well have to get my christmas shopping done sometime this week, so that should be real fun (not) oh well time to go go go

Well, at work now all I hear are the same songs, just sung by different people, and there is only one I like, i think it is enya and she sings silent night, it is actually very cool. Other than that though i am getting sick of christmas, except for the show The Office, they had a christmas special last night and it was hillarious, well i guess thats all for now, nothing really exciting going on in my life, how about all of you???

Well, i just got done watching a pretty good show on the history channel, it was about Edgar Cacey, he was a psychic person who was born in the late eighteen hundreds and lived till 1945. He made a whole bunch of prophecys regarding world war two and even things about the end times, and it seems like his predictions are coming true, it is kind of scary, but he predicted hurricane katrina and all the earthquakes that have been happening, and things get alot worse, he talked about the dead rising from their graves, and land appearing off the eastern seaboard in a twinkiling of an eye, and possibly the tilt of the earths axis is changing, it's kind of freaky, but actually very interesting as well.

Well, today was really boring, didn't really do anything fun, talked to dani, and that wasnt really that exciting, she was talking to her family more than me.....i am not trying to say talk to me NOW, if ur busy, or don't want to talk then just say so. Then i went to meijer to see my friend kathy, and she wasnt there. Oh, i did go and watch walk the line yesterday, and that was really good, it was just a long ass movie though, all the actors did a good job. Well, i guess thats all for now, if anyone wants to do anything tommorow, just give me a call on the cell.

Well, i have been having this urge latley just to go and start killing people, or at least get in a gun fight, i don't know why, it just seems like fun, maybe i am just that bored i guess. lol. Maybe i should just go join WAR, if you don't know what it is then just ask me, but if u do, then label me accordingly, i really don't give a shit. Oh well, my friend liz is going to draw me a picture that i commissioned her for, so that will be pretty sweet, she is a really good artist, and she might be getting a new job, so i am happy for her, because she gets more money, oh well, i guess thats all for now.

Well, my supervisor is taking this whole week off, that is kind of good and kind of bad, first of all i don't have to put up with any of his shit, the bad part is, yesterday i had to unload a 720 piece truck by myself, the other guy who works in recieving was there for the first ten minutes and then for the last fifteen but the two and a half hours in between there was just me unloading the truck, it really sucked, i felt bad for the truck driver, i told him it would be about 2 hrs and it ended up being three, and he dosent get paid just for sitting there in the truck, he gets paid for the ammount of miles he gets. Then my manager is trying to pull shit, saying that we have to get certain things done, that are just too big to get done without my supervisor there, because i would be the only person doing anything again, because the other asshole feels content to just sit back and do nothing. I am sorry for the rant, i just had to get it off my chest, i think i am going to quit, for real this time. There is some good news, i went to the dentist and got my teeth cleaned, so now they feel squeaky clean ^^. Well as far as this weekend goes, i am only busy friday night, if anyone else is bored and wants to hang out just let me know, just don't say your going to call and then not do it. That really gets me mad.

Well this weekend started out good, went out to eat with friends, then went to play halo.Saturday went to see Saw II with my friend Danielle Gierman, so that was alot of fun, it was nice talking to her, and we both have alot of things in commmon, i was thinking i was going to go see a movie with my friends dani, ivy, and possibly david, dani said that she would call me and let me know what was going on, but that never panned out....thats twice lol. Oh well, i guess it was just sunday that was boring, but oh well, hanging out with danielle was the best thing this weekend and that makes up for a boring sunday. Well thats all for now bye byes.

Well, me and my brother just got done watching the tv show the office, it is really funny. It is suppose to be like a reality tv show, but it is extremley funny. We could make one about offcie max easily, and i bet the ratings would be pretty high. Oh well, today pretty much was boring, work then home and nap, and oh yeah, next week my supervisor will not be at work all week, so i might be unloading the truck all by myself, that will really suck alot. I am not even sure how many pieces it will be, hopefully not alot. Friend kevin is being a complete retard, he is 21 and he was giving thie fifteen year old a back rub, fucking dumb ass is going to get thrown in jail, and when his parents don't bail him out, then he will look to me. I am getting sick of alot of people, my friend kelly is being a bitch, i just ask her about how her day went and then, she just blows me off, or just trys to piss me off. Oh well, she is a bitch and i think she is still mad that her bf broke up with her, and it happened exactly as i said it would about a year ago, he just used her and then dumped her. Oh well i guess thats all for now.

Well, here it is halloween, on a monday, wich really sux, cause even if i had something to do i probably wouldnt have been able to do it. It wouldnt be as bad though if certain people weren't being assholes about certain things, I guess there is nothing i can do about that though lol. Well thats all for now, and for those of you out there having a life, more power to you.

Well, it is nice because we all get an extra hour of sleep now, so that is kind of nice, i don't have to be to work until 7:30 tommorow so that is also nice, get to sleep in a little more than normal. This weekend other than friday was pretty uneventful, kind of boring today, just layed around home all day and slept alot ^_^ Also watched a pretty neat thing on the discovery channel about vampires, and there is a vampire association i can join so i can get blood to drink if want, actual human blood, wich i thought was pretty cool. You may think i am crazy, and thats ok, because i probably am. lol well thats all for now

Well i went and watched SAW II today, i fucking loved that movie, and while six people were gettting up and leaving half way through, i was thinking to myself, "I have to meet the people who write this stuff." That was not the highlight of my day however. I got to go see dani in her play, she didn't have a really big part but she was the best actor out there, ok so i am a little bias, but what the hell. Well thats all for now.

well, i was just talking to one of my friends, and we were talking, and i told her that alot of my friends parents hate me. It's the truth, i dont know why they do, they dont even know me, and then my friend told me that i was a bad example. I used to be in highschol, but i have changed damn it. I dont want to be hated by these people, i just am. People don't know me, but they can make assumptions based off what they dont know, so i guess i am better off not hanging out with anyone.....because i am a bad example.

Well, work kind of sucked today, however we did get the truck done, so tommorow should be pretty easy. I am prolly going to see dani's play this friday night/ saturday morning, hopefully i will get to talk to her. I am not sure if i will be going with anyone, or by myself again, oh well, it dosent really matter i guess. Life pretty much sux, i am not sure if my friend kelly is mad at me or not, want to talk to my friend danielle, but i dont get to that much, and i am in a rut where i just feel like i dont want to do anything at all, it sux. I guess i will just have to believe that i my life will turn around at some point, it could be alot worse but it could be alot better too. Well, i guess thats all for now.

It was blocking my background and i was getting really pissed off about it so i decided to take action, and i am victorious, yes i am hahahahahahhahaha take that evil virus things.

Well just got the billy idol greatest hits cd, it is pretty good, and plus it has one of my favortie songs...white wedding on it. I watched a pretty fucked up movie last night, it was called elephant, it was about these teenagers who shot up their school. That gets me thinking back to colombine shooting, i know it is sad, but the kids who dies might as well have shot themselves, because they pushed those kids that far to do something like that. I am not condoing their actions, but it is sad when the teachers knew what was going on, and yet they did nothing, so in my book, i think the kids got what they had coming. You reap what you sow. Also, some kid is in jail, because they found plans in his locker to shoot up the highschool, but the part the media leaves out is that a few weeks before, the football team sodomized him with a broom handle and the coach didnt even do anyting about it. So, he goes to jail while the other kids go free....tell me something is not wrong there.......well thats all for now i guess.

Well....it's finally nice outside agian, it's getting colder, and i can finally see the stars the way i want to. I love looking up at the sky and just thinking. I wish i could go to space, and just feel the emptiness, it must be surreal. Oh well, i went and played halo tonight after eating out with my mom, dad, and aunt and uncle at cladaghs irish pub, it was pretty cool, i had steak, and it was very good and i also got to have some hard cider and the was really good. Well i guess all in all it was a pretty nice night, well thats all for now, i am off to look at the stars again.

Well, it is almost time for me to go to bed and then i am back to work, but this weekend and the past week have been pretty hectic, my friend kathy has been in the hospital since thursday with a blood clot in her lung, but luckily she has been doing alot better, so thats good. I am not sure when she is going to get back to her job though because she really needs the money, because she has to have money for the apartment, but i was sure she was ok because she is tough. Oh well, i guess there really isn't lots happening as the title of this entry implies, but what the hell. Got a new game that me and david are in the progress of beating, Mortal Kombat Shaolin Monks. It is alot of fun, although the camera angles can become kind of annoying after a while and the graphics arent really anything special for an xbox, but the gameplay is where the game really excels. I am really looking forward to the xbox 360 but i need to reserve a game for it too, i am thinking about reserving elder scrolls four oblivion because it looks AWESOME, the graphics are astounding, and i am hoping that the game play is too. As far as friends go, hanging out with david has been fun, kevin just turned 21 so we finished off a fifth of vodka in one night and got kind of drunk....but not bad. Called dani to tell her that kathy was in the hospital, i left a message but she never called back, i am not sure if she is still grounded though.....oh well, i miss talking to her like we did during the summer. Thats all for now....................end transmisson-----outlaw666 out

I have no group to fit in with, i felt like a fourth wheel, they all seemed to have a good time but i was just along for the ride. It hit me on the way back from the mall that i have no one to call my own, i have no place to fit it. There is only one person who i fit in with, my best friend david, we are both wolves looking for our place it seems. It just tears me apart to see everyone has someone else, and they are happy, but i have no one, i am completley alone, i hate it, i dont want to be alone anymore, i dont want to be alone anymore, i dont want to be alone anymore, i hate this feeling, it is so awful, i want only one thing, but it will never happen, because i am not like other people, i have no place, i dont have anyone.........it is so hard not to have a place, i.....just.....dont want to be alone anymore.

I wish i could go to war and get away from all the drama here, over there i would only have to worry about one thing and one thing only, keeping myself alive, not people that i like, not my friends or family, just me. I can't stand it over here any more, friends betraying friends, family members fighting with eachother. I want to go to war, call me insane or stupid, but i need to go to war. I guess this is just the stupid rant of someone who wants to be a part of something important, seeing as i have no one, i wouldnt have anyone to worry about me, besides my family. It just dosent seem that i have been a part of anything big, i want to do my part, i want to fight, and die if necessary. Maybe i will stop taking my meds behind my parents back and then next year join the army, i think that would probably be the best choice, because i am so fucking stupid that i didnt enroll in classes for the fall semester, in the army they pay for at least two years of your college, and you get hands on training, so it's not all fighting and dying.
